I wish I could use Java 11.
Do you like this proposal:
    private String stripEnd(String str, String suffix) {
        int end = str.length();
        if (end == 0 || suffix.isEmpty()) {
            return str;
        }
        while (end > 0 && suffix.indexOf(str.charAt(end - 1)) != -1) {
            end--;
        }
        return str.substring(0, end);
    }

